column2: SELECT TOP # S.z AS redshift, GSL.specobjid, psfmag_g - extinction_g AS g, psfmag_z - extinction_z AS z, GSL.nii_#_flux AS NII, GSL.h_alpha_flux AS Halpha, GSL.oiii_#_flux AS OIII, GSL.h_beta_flux AS Hbeta, GSL.sii_#_flux+GSL.sii_#_flux AS SII, GSL.oi_#_flux AS OI, GSL.neiii_#_flux AS NeIII, GSL.oii_#_flux+GSL.oii_#_flux AS OII FROM SpecObj AS S JOIN galSpecLine AS GSL ON S.specobjid = GSL.specobjid JOIN PhotoObj as p ON p.objid = S.bestobjid AND S.sn1_g > # AND GSL.sigma_balmer < # AND GSL.h_alpha_eqw < # AND GSL.h_beta_eqw < # AND GSL.oiii_#_eqw < # AND GSL.oi_#_eqw< # AND GSL.nii_#_eqw < # AND GSL.sii_#_eqw < # AND GSL.sii_#_eqw < # AND psfmag_g - extinction_g > # AND psfmag_z - extinction_z > # AND S.z BETWEEN # AND #
